WEBVTT

00:04:59.475 --> 00:05:03.841
Ikanijia kua ingekua
ajabu hata hivyo,

00:05:03.865 --> 00:05:06.245
kwa Yesu kurudi tena na tena

00:05:06.269 --> 00:05:07.905
kulingana na kutofautiana mda.

00:05:07.929 --> 00:05:13.242
(Kicheko)

00:05:15.037 --> 00:05:17.210
Na hii ilinifanya nijihisi
mjinga zaidi --

00:05:18.354 --> 00:05:19.555
kuumia, kweli.

00:05:21.076 --> 00:05:24.245
Lakini hapo huo usiku,
sikuacha kuamini.

00:05:25.197 --> 00:05:26.781
Niliamini tu kitu kipya:

00:05:27.487 --> 00:05:29.919
kua inawezekana kutokuamini.